(61, 1, '2016-10-12 03:28:32', '2016-10-12 03:28:32', '<strong>Expected Results:</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Result-1:</strong> Seven community-owned fully equipped ICT centres including necessary infrastructure offer services through skilled work force to people living in 35 nearby villages for getting public and private information.\r\n\r\n<strong>Result – 2:</strong> Seven Local Alliance/Forums formed and alliance/forum members extend support to create mass awareness and demand for info and facilitate demand driven service delivery, coordination, resource generation from the local community.\r\n\r\n<strong>Result-3: </strong>Interactive web portal with provision for news feeds developed and uploaded and ICT services are available at the community level.\r\n\r\n<strong>Result-4: </strong>Regular coordination and networking with like minded ICT centers including service providing agencies for service improvement.\r\n\r\n<strong>Recult-5: </strong>Each ICT generate income to contribute operational cost and for sustainability.', 'Results', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'results', '', '', '2016-10-12 03:28:32', '2016-10-12 03:28:32', '', 42, 'http://localhost/epsppr_project/?page_id=61', 0, 'page', '', 0),
