(63, 1, '2016-10-12 03:29:20', '2016-10-12 03:29:20', '<strong>Major Activities/What does the project do:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Makes community people aware about importance and advantages of information and RTI Act 2009 through street dramas, debate competition, information fairs and village/group meetings;</li>\r\n 	<li>Provides all information free of charge;</li>\r\n 	<li>Provides different ICT related services with charge;</li>\r\n 	<li>Networking/linkage between like minded organizations, local Government Organizations, etc. with Alliances/Forums of ICT centers through meetings ;</li>\r\n 	<li>Campaigns for enrolling members for ICT centers;</li>\r\n 	<li>Provides basic computer trainings;</li>\r\n 	<li>Organizes meetings between staffs and members of Alliances/Forums, MCs and YCs.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Major  Activities', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'major-activities', '', '', '2016-10-12 03:29:20', '2016-10-12 03:29:20', '', 42, 'http://localhost/epsppr_project/?page_id=63', 0, 'page', '', 0),
