(65, 1, '2016-10-12 03:30:03', '2016-10-12 03:30:03', '<strong>Forum/Alliance</strong>\r\n\r\nEvery ICT center has one Alliance/Forum to run the ICT center jointly and facilitate for arranging different project events. Besides, they are building good network and relationship with local government institutions and other like minded organizations through Tri-monthly meetings. Each Alliance/Forum has 10 member selected by the local community people. 40% of the Alliance/Forum members are female. Alliance/Forum operates by following its guideline.', 'Forum/Alliance', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'forumalliance', '', '', '2016-10-12 03:30:03', '2016-10-12 03:30:03', '', 42, 'http://localhost/epsppr_project/?page_id=65', 0, 'page', '', 0),
